      "name": "rum",
      "amount": "1 tablespoon",
      "notes": "for flambe"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the lentils and cook them in a large pot of boiling water until they are tender",
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat and saute the chopped onion until it is translucent",
    "Add the chopped carrots to the skillet and continue to cook until they are tender",
    "Add the cumin to the skillet and cook for 1 minute",
    "Add the cooked lentils, rice, and cod fillet to the skillet and stir to combine",
    "Flambe the mixture by adding the rum and igniting it with a match",
    "Stir in the lemon juice and cook for an additional 2 minutes",
    "Top the mujadara with miniature marshmallows and serve immediately"
  ],
